!:mime	video/x-ifo
!:ext	ifo/bup
>0x21	byte		x		v%x
0	string		DVDVIDEO-VMG	Video manager,
!:mime	video/x-ifo
!:ext	ifo/bup
>0x21	byte		x		v%x

# From: Stefan A. Haubenthal <polluks@sdf.lonestar.org>
