0	string	APS10			APS patch file
!:ext	aps
>5	byte	0			\b, simple patch
>5	byte	1			\b, N64-specific patch for
>>58	byte	x			N%c
>>59	byte	x			\b%c
>>60	byte	x			\b%c
>7	byte	!0x20
# FIXME: /T specifier isn't working with a fixed-length string.
